title: NFL Divisional-Round Weekend, Part 1
description:
Kevin Clark and Ryen Russillo are joined by Mallory Rubin as they instantly react to the Ravens' loss to the Bills (1:05). Later, Kevin and Russillo discuss the Packers' victory over the Rams (16:40).
